    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is powered by the naturally aspirated 3.6L M96 flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The G96 six-speed manual transaxle provides tactile gear synchronization, delivering power to the rear wheels via a robust drivetrain. The chassis retains its factory damping characteristics with MacPherson front struts and a multi-link rear setup, ensuring precise lateral stability. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over vented, cross-drilled rotors for superior heat dissipation. This example has been maintained with an eye toward mechanical longevity, including preventative IMS bearing and RMS inspections. It presents as a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car with minor cosmetic patina reflecting its honest service history.",
